Notes
=====

This plugin allows you to search and replace text in wiki pages.

You can access the page search & replace form through the
Admin system > Wiki Replace.

Find::
  text to find
Replace::
  text to substitute
Wiki Pages::
  a list of wiki pages, each page should be on a separate line;
  you may use * and ? wildcards

  examples: \*, Trac\*, Category/\*/Index, Calendar/2009\_??\_02

TracAdmin command
=================

The TracAdmin command takes the usual form::

    trac-admin $env wiki sub <oldtext> <newtext> <page1> [page2] ...

Permissions
===========

A ``WIKI_REPLACE`` permission is available, though anyone with
``WIKI_ADMIN`` will also be allowed to replace in pages.

Configuration
=============

To enable the plugin::

    [components]
    wikireplace.* = enabled
